			h3 Description
			if (course && course.content)
				| #{course.content}
		.tab-pane.fade#material
			h3 Material
			ul
				li Course Forums
				li CS101 Unit 1 Notes
				li CS101 Unit 1 Glossary
				li CS101 Unit 1 Python Reference

